00:50:08,272 --> 00:50:11,876
♪ [trumpet fanfare] ♪

941
00:50:11,876 --> 00:50:19,717
♪ [throbbing bass, strings &
powerful vocal chorus] ♪

942
00:50:19,717 --> 00:50:50,114
♪    ♪

943
00:50:50,114 --> 00:50:54,985
LORD, WE CLAIM
THIS FIELD FOR YOU TODAY.

944
00:50:54,985 --> 00:50:57,454
THIS IS YOUR BATTLE NOT OURS.

945
00:50:57,454 --> 00:51:00,591
WE PRAY FOR A PEACEFUL
RESOLUTION TO THIS CONFLICT.

946
00:51:00,591 --> 00:51:04,628
WE PRAY FOR COMPLETE
RECONCILIATION AND FORGIVENESS.

947
00:51:04,628 --> 00:51:08,832
LORD, WE BELIEVE THAT
YOU ARE IN TOTAL CONTROL.

948
00:51:08,832 --> 00:51:14,204
AND LORD, PLEASE MAKE ME
TOTALLY INVISIBLE.

949
00:51:16,140 --> 00:51:17,841
WE'RE GOING TO
DESTROY YOU GUYS!

